 it."],[4379,4525,"It is going to be me."],[4525,4667,"And you didn't want to help them"],[4667,4758,"because you wanted"],[4758,4959,"to stay on my good side."],[5005,5196,"Okay, well. It's gonna take a lot"],[5196,5267,"more than that to"],[5267,5384,"stay on my good side,"],[5484,5584,"if you know what I mean."],[5689,5793,"I've always had a thing"],[5793,5993,"for powerful women."],[6018,6093,"It's just something"],[6093,6197,"about making them"],[6389,6548,"surrender to me."]],"50":[[25,225,"We'll see now, won't we?"],[984,1184,"Wait."],[1468,1668,"When you go through that door,"],[1693,1822,"everything will change."],[1822,1985,"Jack, what's going on?"],[1985,2185,"No matter what happens next,"],[2193,2356,"however our lives change,"],[2356,2414,"I just"],[2414,2473,"want you two to know"],[2473,2527,"that I have been"],[2527,2723,"so lucky to have you in my life."],[2848,3011,"I don't need the money."],[3011,3140,"I don't need the fancy houses"],[3140,3299,"or the fancy cars."],[3299,3382,"All I need are the two"],[3382,3541,"loves of my life."],[3541,3724,"I love you."],[3724,3924,"I love you too, sweetie."],[3953,4129,"When I'm with you two,"],[4129,4250,"I feel like the richest man"],[4250,4450,"on the face of the earth."],[4763,4963,"It's time."],[5063,5092,"Yeah..."],[5150,5209,"Let's go."]],"51":[[0,150,"Ladies and gentlemen,"],[150,308,"without further ado,"],[308,408,"it is my honor"],[408,633,"to introduce you to the new CEO"],[646,846,"of Prestige Industries."],[1121,1322,"You're so fucked."],[1351,1488,"Both figuratively"],[1488,1689,"and soon."],[1701,1901,"Literally."],[1906,2164,"And his family."],[2235,2435,"Family?"],[2669,2869,"It's time."],[2948,3098,"Yeah."],[3098,3253,"Let's go."],[3378,3599,"And his family..."],[4166,4295,"Coincidentally, I happen"],[4295,4412,"to be the richest man on"],[4412,4508,"the face of the earth."]],"52":[[0,166,"Ladies and gentlemen,"],[166,321,"it is my pleasure"],[321,525,"to introduce you to Jack Parker,"],[5